snippet.title: Astrobase Command - Closed Alpha - New Features Video #1
snippet.description:
New features in Astrobase Command.

Astrobase Command is a 3D space station builder simulation game which is currently in  Closed Alpha.

To find out more go to:
http://www.astrobasecommand.com/

To join the community come to:
https://discord.gg/jellyfishgames

To support us in our efforts, check out:
https://patreon.com/jellyfishgames
